{"tid":484933,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶森林好正...","createTime":"2017-11-30T13:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T18:20:23.000Z","uid":130849,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f06149a7a27167eba8a9b082e06e30ca7e9ded","tid":484933,"uid":130849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"第一次睇 飛晒王菲打掃果part 有d重要對白都skip埋 細節位自然睇唔到 就覺得好悶咁套戲 <br />\n但第二次睇 全部睇晒無skip 覺得勁正... 成日就係到諗套戲 好沉醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後再上網睇下D人點講 又去睇返我無留意D人所講既細節位 真係覺得王家衛拍得好好 而且90年代味都好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配樂方面都做得好好 首 California dreamin' 好洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋呢 未睇D人評論前 唔明林青霞果段係做咩 兼且覺得D鏡頭同音樂好唔舒服 睇完後明佢用意 雖然都中意金城武既對白 但係記得有人講話 佢咁既樣 唔似會經歷呢D野 無咩代入感 我都有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以最中意都係朝偉同王菲條線<br />\n《春光乍洩》&amp;《重慶森林》都係我永遠唔會睇厭既戲黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好中意 最近又翻睇左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fcf8008455f2508182fb2240ead116521824de","tid":484933,"uid":14652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始，所有野都加左一個日期"},{"pid":"230ba30e2da2f13adfa4b05de1ab55bfd3603f05","tid":484933,"uid":130849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知幾時開始，所有野都加左一個日期</blockquote><br />\n連保鮮紙都會過期，我開始懷疑係呢個世界上，仲有咩係唔會過期？"},{"pid":"dab360fd6112aae97c269fa3fb02ef9a33a536bc","tid":484933,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"點解飛左王菲part？"},{"pid":"4a8d5cc8efdd1830cb8b43c4b747928a92e3e062","tid":484933,"uid":130849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解飛左王菲part？</blockquote><br />\n開頭第一次睇覺得佢打掃果part好悶 好似無咩特別咁 <br />\n應該係因為同人一齊睇 所以無咁投入  因為第二次我都全部無飛咁睇晒 仲好投入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8846dc22814412c371fecdb48332f6c0d9466e","tid":484933,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"同好<br />\n超鍾意苗僑偉果條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d166a22d53d741a823434c614c50098e595f1f","tid":484933,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"又係拋對白時間"},{"pid":"494597de211e61652fa883cfccca121c1c007952","tid":484933,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"好地地轉咩炸魚薯條"},{"pid":"7ea9d50bfc80d84aae16c97e711d6ffe464d6945","tid":484933,"uid":130849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同好<br />\n超鍾意苗僑偉果條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n苗僑偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad82d0956f421075decb63ff47aeec5cabbfc137","tid":484933,"uid":17599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"做咩呢排好似成日都見到重慶森林post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f24c180c96c699de360eef474a530d9c95a5e6","tid":484933,"uid":130849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩呢排好似成日都見到重慶森林post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a20bb2f62e52fe25f82ffa3b3e90569abcf570","tid":484933,"uid":150021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"罐頭菠蘿 and 落雨跑步 好浪漫 意境好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br /